      "text": "あ、あった！\nラッキー、まだ一つだけ残ってたわ",
      "startTime": 3.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子のグッズってほとんどがサニピに入ってからので\nソロ時代のは、もうネットでも売ってなくて",
      "startTime": 10.899987793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、遙子さんのファンだったんですか？",
      "startTime": 13.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "サニピより前の、ソロ時代の遙子の動画も観ましたけど\n正直、冴えないもいいとこでしたね",
      "startTime": 22.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、グッズだけは凝っててセンスが良かったので\n現物を見てみたかったんです",
      "startTime": 30.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（そう言えば昔、遙子さんにグッズのことを相談されて）\n（一緒に考えたことがあったっけ……）",
      "startTime": 36.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら遙子さんに直接頼めば良かったのでは？\n多分まだ一通り持ってると思いますけど",
      "startTime": 43.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、借り物を分解する訳にはいかないでしょ\nそのくらいは自分で買いますよ",
      "startTime": 51.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……なんか、俺一人で勘違いしてたみたいですね\nてっきり麻奈に興味があるものだとばかり……",
      "startTime": 58.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "……長瀬麻奈ねぇ\nすずに借りた資料も見ましたけど、正直……",
      "startTime": 64.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、{user}さんに言うことでもないか",
      "startTime": 69.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "別に、何を言っても怒りはしませんよ",
      "startTime": 73.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか？　基本給を下げたり\nイベントのギャラから余計にピンハネしたりしません？",
      "startTime": 81.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "しません、っていうか今もしてません！",
      "startTime": 84.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ言いますけど\n正直、普通でした",
      "startTime": 90.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "歌はうまかったですし、才能もあるとは思いましたよ\nでも、そこまで騒ぐほどかというと……",
      "startTime": 98.6999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.7999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "ああでも、活動期間あまり長くなかったんでしたっけ\n新人と考えれば、かなりいい線いってる方だったのかな",
      "startTime": 107.3333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.9999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "あと、飾らない感じが良かったですね\n人気出そうなキャラなのはなんとなく分かります",
      "startTime": 115.2333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.4666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、でも……下手じゃないですけど\nあれなら、今のサニピの方が凄くないですか？",
      "startTime": 123.1333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
