      "text": "話が長くて、本当にすみませんでした……",
      "startTime": 153.4999989828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.3666656495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_03-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "確かに長瀬麻奈って人は\n『何か』鮮烈な印象を残すだけのものを持っていて",
      "startTime": 160.3999928792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_antique-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "antique-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.7666656495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
